# Private package resolution for @syncsalez-dev/* — sync-core and
# sync-rn live on GitHub Packages, not the public npm registry.
#
# Auth comes from the GITHUB_TOKEN env var on your shell (or
# ~/.npmrc with `//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=<pat>`). The PAT
# needs the `read:packages` scope. Never commit a token here —
# this file is tracked.

@syncsalez-dev:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_TOKEN}
